    <item>
      <title>१० वर्ण-वृत्तिः, दण्डः</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sUtram/ApastambaH/dharma-sUtram/sarva-prastutiH/2/05/10_varNa-vRttiH_daNDaH/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sUtram/ApastambaH/dharma-sUtram/sarva-prastutiH/2/05/10_varNa-vRttiH_daNDaH/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;0&#34; title=&#34;विश्वास-प्रस्तुतिः&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sUtram/ApastambaH/dharma-sUtram/vishvAsa-prastutiH/2/05/10/01_bhixaNe_nimittamAchAryo_vivAho.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h0&gt;विश्वास-प्रस्तुतिः …{Loading}…&lt;/h0&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;भिक्षणे निमित्तमाचार्यो विवाहो यज्ञो मातापित्रोर्बुभूर्षार्हतश्च नियमविलोपः १&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include collapsed&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;4&#34; title=&#34;सर्वाष् टीकाः&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sUtram/ApastambaH/dharma-sUtram/sarvASh_TIkAH/2/05/10/01_bhixaNe_nimittamAchAryo_vivAho.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;सर्वाष् टीकाः …{Loading}…&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;Bühler&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;The reasons for (which) begging (is permissible are), (the desire to collect the fee for) the teacher, (the celebration of) a wedding, (or of) a Śrauta-sacrifice, the desire to keep one&amp;rsquo;s father and mother, and the (impending) interruption of ceremonies performed by a worthy man. &lt;sup id=&#34;fnref:1&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#fn:1&#34; class=&#34;footnote-ref&#34; role=&#34;doc-noteref&#34;&gt;1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;हरदत्त-टीका&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;सूत्रम्&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;भिक्षणे निमित्तमाचार्यो विवाहो यज्ञो मातापित्रोर्बुभूर्षाऽर्हतश्च नियमविलोपः ॥१॥&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>११ मार्गदानम्, विवाहः</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sUtram/ApastambaH/dharma-sUtram/sarva-prastutiH/2/05/11_mArgadAnam_vivAhaH/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sUtram/ApastambaH/dharma-sUtram/sarva-prastutiH/2/05/11_mArgadAnam_vivAhaH/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;0&#34; title=&#34;विश्वास-प्रस्तुतिः&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sUtram/ApastambaH/dharma-sUtram/vishvAsa-prastutiH/2/05/11/01_itareShAM_varNAnAmA_prANaviprayogAtsamavexya.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h0&gt;विश्वास-प्रस्तुतिः …{Loading}…&lt;/h0&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;इतरेषां वर्णानामा प्राणविप्रयोगात्समवेक्ष्य तेषां कर्माणि राजा दण्डम्प्रणयेत् १&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include collapsed&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;4&#34; title=&#34;सर्वाष् टीकाः&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sUtram/ApastambaH/dharma-sUtram/sarvASh_TIkAH/2/05/11/01_itareShAM_varNAnAmA_prANaviprayogAtsamavexya.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;सर्वाष् टीकाः …{Loading}…&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;Bühler&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;In the cases of (men of) other castes, the king, after having examined their actions, may punish them even by death.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;हरदत्त-टीका&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;सूत्रम्&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;इतरेषां वर्णानामा प्राणविप्रयोगात्समवेक्ष्य तेषां कर्माणि राजा दण्डं प्रणयेत् ॥१॥&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;प्रस्तावः&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;एवं ब्राह्मणविषये उक्तम् । इतरेषामाह -&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;टीका&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;इतरेषां ब्राह्मणव्यतिरिक्तानां वर्णानां राजा पुरोहितोक्तं दण्डं स्वयमेव प्रणयेत् तेषां कर्माणि समवेक्ष्य तदनुरूपमा प्राणविप्रयोगात् । अभिविधाधाकारः ॥१॥&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>१२ अभिनिमृक्तादि</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sUtram/ApastambaH/dharma-sUtram/sarva-prastutiH/2/05/12_abhinimRktAdi/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sUtram/ApastambaH/dharma-sUtram/sarva-prastutiH/2/05/12_abhinimRktAdi/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;0&#34; title=&#34;विश्वास-प्रस्तुतिः&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sUtram/ApastambaH/dharma-sUtram/vishvAsa-prastutiH/2/05/12/01_shaktiviShayeNa_dra_vyANi.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h0&gt;विश्वास-प्रस्तुतिः …{Loading}…&lt;/h0&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;शक्ति-विषयेण द्रव्याणि दत्वा वहेरन् - स आसुरः १&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include collapsed&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;4&#34; title=&#34;सर्वाष् टीकाः&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sUtram/ApastambaH/dharma-sUtram/sarvASh_TIkAH/2/05/12/01_shaktiviShayeNa_dra_vyANi.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;सर्वाष् टीकाः …{Loading}…&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;Bühler&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;If the suitor pays money (for his bride) according to his ability, and marries her (afterwards), that (marriage is called) the Āsura-rite. &lt;sup id=&#34;fnref:1&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#fn:1&#34; class=&#34;footnote-ref&#34; role=&#34;doc-noteref&#34;&gt;1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;हरदत्त-टीका&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;सूत्रम्&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;शक्तिविषयेण द्रव्याणि दत्वाऽऽवहरेन् स आसुरः ॥१॥&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;टीका&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;यत्र विवाहे कन्यावते यथाशक्ति द्रव्याणि दत्त्वाऽऽवहेरन् कन्यां स आसुरः । &lt;sup id=&#34;fnref:2&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#fn:2&#34; class=&#34;footnote-ref&#34; role=&#34;doc-noteref&#34;&gt;2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt; &amp;lsquo;वित्तेनाऽऽनतिस्त्रीमतामासुर&amp;rsquo; इति गौतमः। तेन कन्यायै गृहक्षेत्राभरणादिदानेन विवाहो नाऽऽसुरः ॥१॥&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;0&#34; title=&#34;विश्वास-प्रस्तुतिः&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sUtram/ApastambaH/dharma-sUtram/vishvAsa-prastutiH/2/05/12/02_duhitRmataH_prothayitvA_vaheransa.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h0&gt;विश्वास-प्रस्तुतिः …{Loading}…&lt;/h0&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;दुहितृमतः प्रोथयित्वा वहेरन् - स राक्षसः २&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
